ttp_template:
<group name="model_number">
  Model Number {{MODEL_NUMBER | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="serial_number">
  Serial Number {{SERIAL_NUMBER | re("\\w+")}}
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value SLOT (\d+)
Value DESCRIPTION (.+)
Value MODEL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value SERIAL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value HARDWARE_REVISION (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Slot\s+${SLOT}:\s*$$
  ^\s*Description\s+${DESCRIPTION}\s*$$
  ^\s*Model Number\s+${MODEL_NUMBER}\s*$$
  ^\s*Serial Number\s+${SERIAL_NUMBER}\s*$$
  ^\s*Hardware Revision\s+${HARDWARE_REVISION}\s*$$ -> Record
